      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">3</infon>
        <offset>278</offset>
        <text>Here we show that already before cell lysis the leakage or excretion of organic matter by infected yet intact algal cells shaped North Sea bacterial community composition and enhanced bacterial substrate assimilation.
</text>
